# MCP Scooter - Project Rules

## Project Identity

MCP Scooter is a lightweight, native desktop application that serves as the universal "Operating System" for the Model Context Protocol (MCP). It manages AI tool integrations through a registry system.

**License:** PolyForm Shield 1.0.0 (source-available, non-compete)

